1970-01-01 00:45:00 Preheat your oven to 180 °C or Gas Mark 5

Grease a loaf baking tin and insert a liner

In a bowl mash the ripened bananas until there are no lumps

In a separate large mixing bowl, add all the ingredients and mix until the y are all together and not separated.

Pour into the baking tin and put into the oven for 45-50 minutes

Use a skewer to ensure the mix is cooked throughout and then put on a tray to cool before serving.
